		<div class="irctc_faq">
			<h2>How can I book an IRCTC tour package?</h2>
			<p>Book the best tour packages easily on IRCTC’s official
				website. Click on ‘Holidays’ on the homepage and select
				‘Packages’. Then choose from a range of land, air, and rail tour
				packages and book your dream holiday in a jiffy.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="irctc_faq2">
			<h2>What does a tour package include?</h2>
			<p>A tour package is a complete product that includes a variety
				of services such as transport, accommodation, meals, etc. so that
				tourists can explore a destination hassle-free. A tour package can
				be customized according to the user’s requirements.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="irctc_faq">
			<h2>What is IRCTC insurance policy?</h2>
			<p>Passengers can insure their train journeys in just 59 paise
				including GST while booking their e-ticket through IRCTC. This
				travel insurance is worth up to Rs. 10 lakhs in case of death or
				permanent total disability and Rs. 7.5 lakhs in case of partial
				disability.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="irctc_faq2">
			<h2>How can i book my retiring room in IRCTC?</h2>
			<p>All you need to do is go to the homepage of the IRCTC Tourism
				website, select ‘Retiring Rooms’ and then book a room of your
				choice.In case of queries, you can write to retiringroom@irctc.co.in</p>
		</div>
		<div class="irctc_faq">
			<h2>What is Swadesh Darshan train?</h2>
			<p>One of the most loved and affordable tourist trains in the
				country, Swadesh Darshan covers some of India’s most important
				tourist destinations. It is perfect for travelers and religious
				pilgrims who wish to explore India on a budget.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="irctc_faq2">
			<h2>Some of the famous religious IRCTC tour package?</h2>
			<p>IRCTC Tourism offers tour packages for religious pilgrims.Some
				of the most popular ones include Jyotirlinga Yatra,Dakshin Bharat
				Yatra with Balaji Darshan,Dwarkadhish Jyotirlinga Yatra,Jagannath
				Dham,Ramayana Tour and Mata Vaishno Devi Darshan among others.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="irctc_faq">
			<h2>How can i book a hotel through IRCTC?</h2>
			<p>Visit the official IRCTC Tourism website and click on ‘IRCTC
				Hotels’ on the homepage. From budget hotels to deluxe stays, you
				will find a range of hotels that can be booked easily using your
				IRCTC account.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="irctc_faq2">
			<h2>How can i book a domestic and international tour package</h2>
			<p>Both domestic and international tour packages are available on
				IRCTC Tourism.Visit official IRCTC Tourism website and below the
				search bar select domestic or international according to your
				requirement.Then click on ‘Search’ and you will be shown a list
				of well-planned packages.</p>
		</div>
